1
00:00:00,800 --> 00:00:04,166
Have you ever wondered what life looks like 
on the far side of the Earth?

2
00:00:04,600 --> 00:00:06,633
Welcome to Antipode: DayDreamNight,

3
00:00:06,633 --> 00:00:11,333
a breakthrough social video experience that connects people across day and night 

4
00:00:11,333 --> 00:00:15,866
Inspired by antipodes— 
two places on Earth that lie directly opposite each other.

5
00:00:16,033 --> 00:00:20,266
On the Home feed, each video captures a real moment from another part of the world,

6
00:00:20,266 --> 00:00:21,866
 with a switchable Day–Night mode.

7
00:00:22,066 --> 00:00:24,433
Navigation is intuitive and effortless:

8
00:00:24,566 --> 00:00:25,933
 swipe left to skip,

9
00:00:26,033 --> 00:00:28,766
swipe up or down to move between moments,

10
00:00:28,766 --> 00:00:32,333
and swipe right to appreciate and open a creator's profile.

11
00:00:32,433 --> 00:00:37,233
You can also interact naturally: emojis, comment, or share videos with friends. 

12
00:00:37,366 --> 00:00:39,966
Creating your own moment is just as seamless.

13
00:00:39,966 --> 00:00:44,066
Switch cameras, record, pause, or save drafts effortlessly.

14
00:00:44,066 --> 00:00:47,500
Add tags, text, and share your perspective with the world.

15
00:00:47,833 --> 00:00:51,433
Stay connected through your Friends feed and expressive user profiles.

16
00:00:51,433 --> 00:00:55,200
Chat brings conversations to life with clear, modern messaging.

17
00:00:55,200 --> 00:01:01,266
On the Profile page, users can explore creators through clean galleries of grids, drafts, and tagged videos.

18
00:01:01,266 --> 00:01:04,100
And to ensure everyone can enjoy the experience…

19
00:01:04,100 --> 00:01:07,700
Antipode supports diverse viewing needs with 
screen narration, 

20
00:01:07,700 --> 00:01:11,433
subtitles, high-contrast mode and flexible display options.

21
00:01:11,433 --> 00:01:16,833
Users can fine-tune playback with adjustable brightness, contrast, saturation, and speed.

22
00:01:16,866 --> 00:01:20,333
And the interface adapts naturally to different screen sizes.

23
00:01:20,333 --> 00:01:25,300
Keyboard controls make navigation easy on desktop with simple arrow-key shortcuts.

24
00:01:25,300 --> 00:01:27,800
We welcome users from every corner of the world.

25
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:33,700
The interface and subtitles can switch languages—English or Chinese—for a familiar, comfortable experience.

26
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:39,833
Antipode opens a new way to experience life across the globe—turning everyday stories into global connections.

27
00:01:39,833 --> 00:01:43,400
Our interactive prototype is complete and ready for presentation.

28
00:01:43,600 --> 00:01:44,966
Thank you for watching.

